{
  "name": "WF3 — Missed Appointment Recovery",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 3: Missed Appointment Recovery\n\n**Trigger:** Daily at 10:00 AM\n\n**Logic (from Supabase):**\n- Day +1: Empathetic recovery message (template: patient_missed_recovery)\n- Day +3: Second nudge referencing the doctor (template: patient_missed_nudge)\n- Day +7: Marks patient status as `missed` in Supabase (stops messaging)\n\nReads ONLY from Supabase `public.patients`.\n\n**Before activating:**\n1. Set credential on all Postgres nodes → Supabase DB\n2. Set credential on HTTP nodes → Twilio Basic Auth\n3. Ensure both `patient_missed_recovery` and `patient_missed_nudge` templates are approved",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 400
      },
      "id": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        240,
        60
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 10 * * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-000000000002",
      "name": "Daily 10AM Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [
        240,
        380
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "executeQuery",
        "query": "SELECT p.* FROM public.patients p WHERE p.follow_up_date < CURRENT_DATE AND p.status NOT IN ('completed','inactive')",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-000000000003",
      "name": "Read Patients from Supabase",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.postgres",
      "typeVersion": 2.4,
      "position": [
        460,
        380
